description:
All right good morning Morning Show family I'm a 28 year old working pregnant woman. Well here is my problem. I began dating a friend of three years about a year ago when he resurfaced in my life. He was in the midst of a rough time where due to tragedy he lost almost everything he owned. Being the kind and giving soul that I am I offered my help.
